<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>

  <!-- Basic Page Needs
  –––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>so-sure - Social mobile phone insurance. Better, cheaper, easier.</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Social mobile phone insurance made better, easier and up to 80% cheaper. The social insurance revolution starts here." />
  <meta name="keywords" content="mobile insurance, phone insurance, mobile phone insurance, cheap mobile phone insurance, cheap phone insurance, cheap mobile insurance, better phone insurance, better mobile phone insurance" />

  <!-- FB Open Graph Tags
  –––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
  {% if referral !=  '' %}
    {% set og_title = 'Join today & get rewarded' %}
    {% set og_image = 'https://cdn.so-sure.com/images/home/so-sure-simply-amazing-cta.png' %}
  {% endif %}

  {% include 'AppBundle:Default:header.html.twig' %}

</head>

<body>
  <!-- Facebook Pixel Code
  –––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
  <noscript><img height="1" width="1" style="display:none" src="https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=1018444924864481&ev=PageView&noscript=1" /></noscript>

  <!-- Primary Page Layout
  –––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
  <div class="section hero">
    <div class="container">
      <img class="logo" src="images/logo/so-sure-logo-new-light.svg"></img>
      <h2 class="section-title">Simply amazing insurance.</h2>
      <div class="signup">
        {{ form_start(form_top) }}
        {{ form_widget(form_top.email, {'attr': {'class': 'email', 'placeholder': 'Enter your email'}}) }}
        {{ form_widget(form_top.save, {'label': 'Signup', 'attr': {'class': 'button button-primary'}}) }}
        {{ form_end(form_top) }}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="learn-more">
      <p>LEARN MORE</p>
      <span class="chevron bottom"></span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section how">
    <div class="container">
      <h3 class="section-heading">Why we're better</h3>
      <p class="section-description">We're committed to making it as easy as possible for you and your friends to get covered, get rewarded and make a claim.</p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="one-third column">
          <h2><img src="/images/icons/lock.svg"></img></h2>
          <h5 class="section-heading">You're covered</h5>
          <p class="section-description">For a small monthly fee, you're covered for theft, loss, accidental damage, accessories and unauthorised usage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-third column">
          <h2><img src="/images/icons/wallet.svg"></img></h2>
          <h5 class="section-heading">Get up to 80% of your money back</h5>
          <p class="section-description">We'll give you money back at the end of the year when you and up to 8 friends don’t make a claim.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="one-third column">
          <h2><img src="/images/icons/stopwatch.svg"></img></h2>
          <h5 class="section-heading">Next working day replacement</h5>
          <p class="section-description">To claim, give us a call any time and once approved we’ll get a replacement phone to you the next working day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="one-half column">
          <h3 class="section-heading">Social mobile phone insurance. Better, cheaper, easier.</h3>
          <p class="section-description">Get insured, connect to your friends &amp; get rewarded when you don't claim.</p>
          <a class="button button-primary" href="#join-today">Signup today</a>
        </div>
        <div class="one-half column phones">
          <img class="phone" src="images/iphone.png">
          <img class="phone" src="images/nexus.png">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section mission" id="mission">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our mission.</h2>
        <h3 class="section-heading">Insurance is rubbish.</h3>
        <p class="section-description">It costs too much, you're never quite sure what you're paying for and when you try to claim you discover that you didn't read their <small>small print</small>.</p>
        <h3 class="section-heading">We are making it better.</h3>
        <p class="section-description">We're taking insurance back to how it all started: careful, connected people who can trust that when shit does happen, they’re covered. And when it doesn’t, they get most of their money back.
          <br>We call this social insurance.</p>
        <h3 class="section-heading">We are starting with phones.</h3>
        <p class="section-description">Why? Because those shiny, magical objects connect us with the people we <i class="fa fa-heart" alt="love"></i> most.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section twitter">
    <div class="container">
      <h3 class="section-heading">It's time for a change</h3>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="one-third column">
          <blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en">
            <p lang="en" dir="ltr"><a href="https://twitter.com/AskNationwide">@AskNationwide</a> why is your mobile phone insurance claim process via paper and post? <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/1980s?src=hash">#1980s</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/slow?src=hash">#slow</a>              <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/needsarethink?src=hash">#needsarethink</a></p>&mdash; Kerrie Colford (@kerriecolford) <a href="https://twitter.com/kerriecolford/status/684687370843779072">January 6, 2016</a>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="one-third column">
          <blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en">
            <p lang="en" dir="ltr">Bad service <a href="https://twitter.com/AskLloydsBank">@AskLloydsBank</a> Acc upgrade met with advisor saying &quot;computer says no&quot; just cos I didn&#39;t want your mobile insurance bundled in.</p>&mdash; Tom R. (@Tomptati0n) <a href="https://twitter.com/Tomptati0n/status/614420014419083267">June 26, 2015</a>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="one-third column">
          <blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en">
            <p lang="en" dir="ltr">incredibly poor ecommerce experience from <a href="https://twitter.com/EE">@EE</a> apparently if you upgrade via the mobile site, they REMOVE your insurance!</p>&mdash; Robert Nicholson (@RobBothan) <a href="https://twitter.com/RobBothan/status/684056441360105472">January 4, 2016</a>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="section-description">This is why we're commited to giving you the best possible experience.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section cta" id="join-today">
    <div class="container">
      <h3 class="section-heading">Get a better insurance experience.</h3>
      <div class="signup">
        {{ form_start(form_bottom) }}
        {{ form_widget(form_bottom.email, {'attr': {'class': 'email', 'placeholder': 'Enter your email'}}) }}
        {{ form_widget(form_bottom.save, {'label': 'Signup', 'attr': {'class': 'button button-primary'}}) }}
        {{ form_end(form_bottom) }}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {% include 'AppBundle:Default:footer.html.twig' %}

  </div>
  <!-- End Document
  –––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––– -->
</body>

</html>
